*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Report ZMM_LIFTVF
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Lift ASP Verification Report
*& Displays data from ZLIFT_ASP table in ALV format
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Created by: [Your Name]
*& Date: [Date]
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*

REPORT zmm_liftvf.

*--- Include TOP (Data Declarations)
INCLUDE zmm_liftvf_top.

*--- Include SEL (Selection Screen)
INCLUDE zmm_liftvf_sel.

*--- Include F01 (Subroutines)
INCLUDE zmm_liftvf_f01.

*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
*  AT SELECTION-SCREEN Validation
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
AT SELECTION-SCREEN ON BLOCK b1.

  IF s_zp2pdetrno     IS INITIAL AND
     s_zaspwh         IS INITIAL AND
     s_cgi_date       IS INITIAL AND
     s_zinv_party     IS INITIAL AND
     s_itemcode       IS INITIAL AND
     s_zbill_date     IS INITIAL AND
     s_zonsignment_po IS INITIAL.
    MESSAGE 'Enter at least one selection option' TYPE 'E'.
  ENDIF.

*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
*  START-OF-SELECTION
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
START-OF-SELECTION.

  "Fetch data from database
  PERFORM get_data.

*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
*  END-OF-SELECTION
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
END-OF-SELECTION.

  "Display ALV report
  PERFORM display.
